metadata.title: The Top Recipients Of Covid-19 R&D Funding
metadata.description: Main recipients of Covid-19 vaccine R&D investments as of March 2021 (in million U.S. dollars)
metadata.main_insight: Moderna Therapeutics, Janssen, and Pfizer/BioNTech were the top three recipients of COVID-19 R&D funding as of March 2021, all receiving over $800 million, primarily from public sources.
